Title: The Legend of the Wu-Tang - The Videos

reviewText: This was a great DVD.  It compiles alot of Wu-Tang's popular videos and it has some great interviews and footage from a '94 performance.  There's alot more videos that we need to see on future DVD's (all their solo videos).  I hope they are planning to release all of them.  I remmember "All I Need" and "Brooklyn Zoo" being two of there most popular videos in terms of how much they were played on TV.  Regardless, this is good DVD to have and it's at a great affordable price.
Title: The Legend of the Wu-Tang - The Videos

reviewText: If you're a Wu-tang fan this is a must have, great videos, a couple of which I've never seen. Great collection.

Title: The Legend of the Wu-Tang - The Videos

reviewText: Great DVD that just got released. This DVD gives you all of the videos just by the Wu-Tang as a group, no solo videos. Then after all those videos are done they have the other version of the "Method Man" video, and the "Masta Killa - Old Man" video.THe best thing this DVD offers is the interviews with them back in 1994. Very rare and good they added that in the video. Then it has small interviews with each member in Wu. A good add for sure. For the price, its definately worth it.This DVD is for WU fans!!!
summary: Legend Of The Wu-Tang - The Videos
